Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:03.40,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背負「自由之翼」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:10.56,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握決意抵在左胸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:15.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}劈裂「愚行之螺旋」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.90,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}翱翔於蒼穹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:24.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自由之翼
